      "role": "user",
      "content": "that sounds like a solid start. let's dive into the dress code part. what would you say are the actual standards for \"professionalism\" and \"sophistication\" in a high-end business setting? like, if i want to give my readers a baseline for what looks truly polished and elite, what should they be aiming for?",
